Cookie-jar: session

###

### ✅ 게시글 좋아요 취소
DELETE http://localhost:8080/likes/feeds/1
Cookie-jar: session

###

### ✅ 댓글 좋아요 등록
POST http://localhost:8080/likes/comments/1
Cookie-jar: session

###

### ✅ 댓글 좋아요 취소
DELETE http://localhost:8080/likes/comments/1
